high_descs: Turn right, go forward to the shelves, turn right, go forward to the plant, turn left, go forward to the table with the lap top.
Close the lap top and take it from the table.
Turn around, go forward, turn right before reaching the box on the left side, go forward between the coffee table and couch to the wall, turn right to face the lamp in the corner.
Turn the lamp in the corner on.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a lap top near a lit lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left and walk across the room, through the doorway, to the desk across from you.
Close and pick up the laptop that is on the desk.
Turn around and walk through the doorway, then turn right and go past the couch, to the lamp in the right corner of the room.
Turn on the lamp in the right corner of the living room, to the left of the couch.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the living room lamp.

high_descs: Turn right at the gray door and turn right before the brown bookshelf on your left and go straight to the table at the end of the hall.
Pick up the laptop on the table.
Turn around and go through the doorway. Turn right as you go through and go to the table in the corner.
Turn on the light on the corner table.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the laptop and bring it to the table and turn on a lamp.
